title: The properties which are not part of DRP as defined above shall be developed in accordance with Regulation No 30 only
clause_text: The properties which are not part of DRP as defined above shall be developed in accordance with Regulation No 30 only. The other provisions of DCR allowing higher FSI which are permitted under Regulation No 33 shall not be applicable to such properties which are not part of DRP.
